y"},{"d":"काले","m":"at a time"},{"d":"रूक्षमारुतम्","m":"fine wea the r"},{"d":"दुर्दिनम्","m":"cloudy"},{"d":"अभवत्","m":"became"},{"d":"सर्वे","m":"all over"},{"d":"खगमृगाः","m":"birds and beasts"},{"d":"क्रूराः","m":"cruel"},{"d":"भयावहाः","m":"frightening"},{"d":"वाचः","m":"words"},{"d":"ऊचुः","m":"cries."}]},{"v":12,"dev":"ससिंहापचित्कन्धःशार्दूलसमविक्रमः तानुत्पातानचिन्स्सैवनिर्जगामरणाजिरम् ।","trans":"He whose shoulders were developed like that of a lion, who equalled tiger in valour, went forth not minding the evil portents.","words":[{"d":"सिंहापचितस्कन्धः","m":"whose shoulders were like that of a lion"},{"d":"शार्दूलसमविक्रमः","m":"equalled tiger in valour"},{"d":"सः","m":"he"},{"d":"तान्","m":"them"},{"d":"उत्पातान्","m":"developed"},{"d":"अविचिन्स्सैव","m":"not minding evil portents"},{"d":"रणाजिरम्","m":"to battle"},{"d":"निर्जगाम","m":"went."}]},{"v":13,"dev":"तथानिर्गच्छतस्तस्यरक्षसस्सहराक्षसैः बभूवसुमहान्नादःक्षोभयन्निवसागरम् ।","trans":"While that Akampana was going like that along with Rakshasas huge noise that arose was as if the ocean was agitated.","words":[{"d":"तस्यरक्षसः","m":"that Rakshasa"},{"d":"राक्षसैःसह","m":"along with Rakshasas"},{"d":"तथा","m":"like that"},{"d":"निर्गच्छदः","m":"going"},{"d":"सागरम्","m":"ocean"},{"d":"क्षोभयन्निव","m":"agitated"},{"d":"सुमहान् नादः","m":"huge noise"},{"d":"बभूव","m":"rose."}]},{"v":14,"dev":"तेनशब्देनवित्रस्तावानराणांमहाचमूः द्रुमशैलप्रहाराणांयोद्धुंसमुपतिष्ठतं ।","trans":"Huge troops of Vanaras holding trees and hillocks stood prepared for waging and by that the noise that arose expanded.","words":[{"d":"द्रुमशैलप्रहाराणाम्","m":"trees and hillocks in hand"},{"d":"वानराणाम्","m":"Vanaras"},{"d":"महाचमूः","m":"huge troops"},{"d":"योद्धुम्","m":"for the combat"},{"d":"समुपतिष्ठतं","m":"stood prepared"},{"d":"तेनशब्देन","m":"by that noise"},{"d":"वित्रस्ता","m":"expanded."}]},{"v":15,"dev":"तेषांयुद्धंमहारौद्रंसञ्जज्ञेकपिरक्षसाम् रामरावणयोरर्धेसमभित्यक्तजीविनाम् ।","trans":"Vanaras and Rakshasas dedi